### Variables
@hostname = localhost
@port = 5001
@baseUrl = http://{{hostname}}:{{port}}

### 1. Test Root Route
GET {{baseUrl}}/
Accept: application/json

###

### 2. Get All Songs
GET {{baseUrl}}/songs
Accept: application/json

###

### 3. Get Song by Id
GET {{baseUrl}}/songs/69c2bb2b977c49ce5bd83987

### 4. Add a New Song
POST {{baseUrl}}/songs
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Bohemian Rhapsody",
    "artist": "Queen",
    "album": "A Night at the Opera"
}

###

### 5. Get All Users
GET {{baseUrl}}/users
Accept: application/json

###

### 6. Register a New User
POST {{baseUrl}}/users/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "aaron_m",
    "email": "aaron@example.com",
    "password": "securePassword123"
}